sys_hub_flow.description:
Adds the client's assets to an existing account closure request using as inputs:
- request_number: The number of the current account closure request.
- client_assets: A A JSON object with the following structure:
{
"products": [
{
"number": "06 010 00 0000011",
"description": "Zurich Bank Conto Welcome",
"type": "current_account"
},
{
"number": "68 010 00 0000011",
"description": "Zurich Finanziamento",
"type": "policy"
}
]
}

